WRITING.TITLE: Is this itinerary possible?
WRITING.TEXT:
This is our jam packed itinerary and I was wondering if it's possible. I was using Google Directions for the times from city to city, so they could be very inaccurate, but from my research they seem kinda close.
Any suggestions or criticisms would be greatly appreciated.
Feb 13: Arrive at night, pick up car. Sleep in Liberia.
Feb 14: Drive to Arenal (2.5 hr drive), arrive ~11am Spend afternoon at volcano, evening in hot springs. Sleep in La Fortuna.
Feb 15: Hike till 11am, drive to Moin (5hr drive) spend night in Moin/Limon area. OR drive to Guapiles/Cariari/La Pavona to catch the boat (boats leave at 7:30am, 1:30pm, 4:30pm)
Feb 16: Early boat to Tortuguero. Spend night in Tortuguero.
Feb 17: Tortuguero. Spend night in Tortuguero.
Feb 18: Early boat to Moin. Drive 1hr to Cahuita/Puerto Viejo. Spend night in either one.
Feb 19: Cahuita to Puerto Viejo (30 min drive). Spend night in either one.
Feb 20: Drive back ALL DAY from Puerto Viejo to Liberia (7 hr drive?)
